                Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Add Companion <gen> (checking conditions)
                -------- ================================ --------
                -------- ================= CHECK that hired unit is less than or equal to level of either Nazgrek or Zul'kis --------
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
                            Conditions
                                CompanionHiredUnitLevel[(Custom value of CompanionUnit[CompanionCount])] Less than or equal to (Hero level of Nazgrek)
                                CompanionHiredUnitLevel[(Custom value of CompanionUnit[CompanionCount])] Less than or equal to (Hero level of Zulkis)
                    Then - Actions
                        -------- Add the hired unit to Companion_Group & Multiboard --------
                        Sound - Play Rescue <gen>
                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Name of (Sold unit)) +  has joined the party!)
                        Unit Group - Add CompanionUnit[CompanionCount] to Companion_Group
                        Unit Group - Add CompanionUnit[CompanionCount] to CompanionFocusNazgrek
                        -------- ================================ --------
                    Else - Actions
                        -------- Hired unit was too high level for the player! --------
                        Set VariableSet CompanionUnitKicked = CompanionUnit[CompanionCount]
                        Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Remove Companion <gen> (checking conditions)
                        -------- ================================ --------
                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: |cFFFF0000Error: |r...
                        -------- ================================ --------
                        Cinematic - Send transmission to (All players) from (Sold unit) named (Name of (Sold unit)): Play No sound and display It looks like your ....  Modify duration: Set to 2.00 seconds and Don't wait
