                        Unit - Change ownership of (Sold unit) to Player 2 (Blue) and Change color
                        Unit - Add a 60.00 second Generic expiration timer to (Sold unit)
                        Set VariableSet CompVarPoint = (Random point in (Playable map area))
                        Unit - Order (Sold unit) to Move To CompVarPoint
                        -------- ================================ --------
                        Custom script:   call RemoveLocation(udg_CompVarPoint)
                        -------- ================================ --------
